description: Today I met a young guy in the metro. He was originally from Slovakia and moved to Prague just recently. It seems to be a trend as I met a couple of Slovak guys over the last months. However, thats fine for me as I adore their looks very much. He came here for work - but so far he didn´t find something. Actually he told me that he just came back from a job interview and though he has this time a good felling he was still very unsure about the outcome. His parents finance his living so far. But they expect it to be paid back. When I heard all of that I was sure that he will be open minded towards my offer. But I decided to proceed step by step. When we arrived at a hotel I noticed that his body looked amazing. And his dick was hard on command. What a beauty...
title: Czech Hunter 224
